    "We also evaluated the parameter efficiency of RED by comparing it with the most parameter-efficient variants of other PEFT methods.",
    "We introduce two operators to edit the hidden representations of neural network models: one scales a hidden representation using a learnable vector, and the other adds a bias vector to the hidden representation.",
